 {"id":"jeffrey_emanuel_personal_site-r0i","title":"Epic: TL;DR Page World-Class UI/UX Overhaul","description":"# TL;DR Page World-Class UI/UX Overhaul

## Overview
Transform the /tldr page from a functional developer-oriented page to a world-class, Stripe-level polished showcase that makes visitors gasp at its sophistication and attention to detail.

## Background & Context
The TL;DR page showcases 13 open-source Flywheel tools. Current implementation is solid but has:
- Several bugs affecting data consistency and accessibility
- Missing interactive features expected in modern UIs
- Mobile experience that's cramped rather than optimized
- Lack of micro-interactions and polish that define premium experiences

## Goals
1. Fix all bugs and accessibility issues (Tier 1)
2. Add high-impact UX features: search, interactive diagram, copy buttons (Tier 2)
3. Add premium polish: animations, visual depth, choreography (Tier 3)
4. Future-proof with advanced features: comparison mode, live data (Tier 4)

## Success Criteria
- Zero accessibility violations (axe-core clean)
- All touch targets ≥44px
- Lighthouse performance score ≥90
- Sub-100ms interaction response times
- Works flawlessly on mobile and desktop
- Visitors comment on the polish and smoothness

## Key Files
- app/tldr/page.tsx - Main page component
- components/tldr-hero.tsx - Hero section with stats
- components/tldr-tool-grid.tsx - Tool card grid with sections
- components/tldr-tool-card.tsx - Individual tool cards
- components/tldr-synergy-diagram.tsx - SVG synergy visualization
- lib/content.ts - Tool data (tldrFlywheelTools, tldrPageData)

## Technical Considerations
- Must respect prefers-reduced-motion throughout
- Must maintain <100KB JS for initial load
- All animations via Framer Motion for consistency
- Mobile-first responsive approach
- No breaking changes to existing URL structure

## Reference Standards
- Stripe.com product pages (micro-interactions, depth)
- Linear.app (keyboard navigation, polish)
- Vercel.com (dark mode excellence, typography)","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-12T22:49:09.758995199Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-06T18:38:03.109094835Z","closed_at":"2026-02-06T18:38:03.109028602Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
